---
title: 应用商店与权限注册池流程
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant Store as APP商店 UI
    participant LocalAPI as 本地权限后端
    participant Kernel as Kernel
    participant DB as IndexedDB
    participant Cloud as 云端 Store API

    Note over User,Cloud: === 浏览商店（推荐） ===
    User->>Store: 打开商店
    Store->>Cloud: GET 应用列表
    Cloud-->>Store: 返回全部公开应用
    Store-->>User: 渲染应用卡片

    Note over User,Cloud: === 浏览商店（已授权） ===
    User->>Store: 切换到"已授权"标签
    Store->>LocalAPI: GET /system/permission/my-authorized-ids
    LocalAPI->>LocalAPI: 查询 permission_cache
    LocalAPI-->>Store: authorized_ids + apps 列表
    Store-->>User: 显示有权限的 APP

    Note over User,Cloud: === 注册到权限池（上传流程） ===
    User->>Store: 上传 APP 时勾选"注册到权限池"
    Store->>Kernel: uploadResource(registryEnabled=true)
    Kernel->>Cloud: 上传到云端 (isPrivate=true)
    Store->>LocalAPI: POST /system/permission/registry (permission_enabled=true)
    LocalAPI->>LocalAPI: register_app()
    LocalAPI->>LocalAPI: 自动添加上传者到 allowed_users
    LocalAPI->>LocalAPI: 更新 D_SukinosApp.registry_enabled=true
    LocalAPI-->>Store: 注册成功

    Note over User,Cloud: === 授权管理（注册池面板） ===
    User->>LocalAPI: PUT /system/permission/registry/{id}/actors
    LocalAPI->>LocalAPI: 更新 actor_rules (黑白名单)
    LocalAPI-->>User: 更新成功

    Note over User,Cloud: === 删除 APP 清理注册池 ===
    User->>Cloud: 删除云端上传
    User->>LocalAPI: POST /system/permission/registry (permission_enabled=false)
    LocalAPI->>LocalAPI: registry_enabled=false
    LocalAPI-->>User: 移除完成

    Note over User,Cloud: === 静态文件访问（授权用户） ===
    User->>Kernel: 打开私有 APP
    Kernel->>LocalAPI: StaticAuthMiddleware
    LocalAPI->>LocalAPI: check_permission(resource_id, user)
    alt 上传者 or 授权用户
        LocalAPI-->>Kernel: 放行
    else 无权限
        LocalAPI-->>Kernel: 403 拒绝
    end